{"tid":151724,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得 2006-2009年係人生最開心 快樂既日子?","createTime":"2017-03-11T06:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T02:36:27.000Z","uid":27200,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edf557bbb4d5c53919c7a3eff0eb593ff9117313","tid":151724,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"人愈大 <br />\n出到黎社會<br />\n發覺愈難擁有真正既快樂<br />\n回望以前2006-2009年<br />\n網路世界岩岩掘起 <br />\n一齊玩MSN qooza xanga個種集體氣氛<br />\n電視劇集潮  一班輕生仔都會一齊追台劇 港劇<br />\n一齊熱血 一齊喊都試過<br />\n以前落街每一個公園都有一班街童霸住<br />\n因為太多人玩「何仔」 所以要排隊<br />\n一齊係樓下成十幾二十人玩「兵捉賊」又試過<br />\n用鋼做既爆旋陀螺爆到人地隻膠陀螺爛左<br />\n講到當年既社會<br />\n家長仲未有「望子成龍」既心態<br />\n唔會逼班細路參加興趣班 又補習班 又日夜溫書<br />\n望見宜家班細路 真係覺得佢地好可憐<br />\n每日30分鐘玩下手機game就當娛樂左<br />\n望住宜家公園既人數就可以感受到個種時代既反差 時代既諷刺<br />\n唔望你地係呢個post得到咩<br />\n希望可以勾起你地以往一絲絲既回億同快樂既感覺<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>奇幻潮</ins></strong><br />\n想當年播完奇幻潮先播鋼鍊<br />\n聽到d背景音樂已經驚到傻<br />\n鼠入被竇到 露對眼出黎偷偷睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image16.poco.cn/mypoco/myphoto/20141106/18/174746717201411061800543694305904425_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage16.poco.cn%2Fmypoco%2Fmyphoto%2F20141106%2F18%2F174746717201411061800543694305904425_001.jpg&h=5de05669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_TNe_cn-NDY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F_TNe_cn-NDY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=1d71b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.k165.com/images/movies/full/63e88743eb8dec2884cbbe9e0bbdb7f25998d623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.k165.com%2Fimages%2Fmovies%2Ffull%2F63e88743eb8dec2884cbbe9e0bbdb7f25998d623.jpg&h=e048d347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/26cdd05e627ffff9e9bdd500ba37c2db/tumblr_oaysrzFLQS1vzwxhdo1_540.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F26cdd05e627ffff9e9bdd500ba37c2db%2Ftumblr_oaysrzFLQS1vzwxhdo1_540.png&h=a83beba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.tvb.com/ii/28/35662/000003566189_1406601141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fii%2F28%2F35662%2F000003566189_1406601141.jpg&h=c01f3c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>台劇</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>惡作劇之吻</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fun-tv.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/%E6%83%A1%E4%BD%9C%E5%8A%87%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fun-tv.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2F%25E6%2583%25A1%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%258A%2587%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2590%25BB.jpg&h=6fcc4953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXwRbqqD78A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGXwRbqqD78A&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9be04d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXwRbqqD78A</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Urwc4rdG28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7Urwc4rdG28&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=68fe7392\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Urwc4rdG28</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>終極一家</strong><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://photocdn.sohu.com/20080516/Img256903905.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotocdn.sohu.com%2F20080516%2FImg256903905.jpg&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ef755aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photocdn.sohu.com/20080516/Img256903905.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twword.com/uploads/wiki/9b/9e/437609_19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twword.com%2Fuploads%2Fwiki%2F9b%2F9e%2F437609_19.jpg&h=cf4c0e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然以前拍攝既畫質無宜家咁細緻咁靚<br />\n但起碼劇組有擺心機落去拍攝<br />\n特別好鐘意d角色設計 每個角色又有異能兵器 鬼龍鎞克、驚雷、麒麟手等等<br />\n個system起碼吸引到人睇<br />\n睇番宜家d劇集 淨係講三角戀<br />\n劇情設計又唔吸引 太過商業化<br />\n<br />\n<strong>命中註定我愛你</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5b/Cutegirl.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5b%2FCutegirl.JPG&h=73b7c67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2009/01/901020959211485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2009%2F01%2F901020959211485.jpg&h=624f66f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kCtAisFDWNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkCtAisFDWNU&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=45130b66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kCtAisFDWNU</a><br />\n首主題曲好懷念阿~~<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XGS1MRYJR2k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXGS1MRYJR2k&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c34619f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XGS1MRYJR2k</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下一站幸福</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.eslite.com/Upload/Product/200910/m/633911290448095710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.eslite.com%2FUpload%2FProduct%2F200910%2Fm%2F633911290448095710.jpg&h=98187bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/l97f9cAd8Vk/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fl97f9cAd8Vk%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=af134603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/K_a_L5kyKwM/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FK_a_L5kyKwM%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=97e75512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年d女同學<br />\nmsn status 改哂做 &quot;米修 米修&quot;<br />\n番學又成日扮個細路講 &quot;米修米修&quot;扮可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsrXbkk5Vdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLsrXbkk5Vdw&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=acd5defe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsrXbkk5Vdw</a><br />\n呢首歌當年紅到痴線<br />\n「我愛他 ~~~ 轟轟烈烈最瘋狂」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>海派甜心</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.go123go.com/uploadfile/2011/1230/20111230055953719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.go123go.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2011%2F1230%2F20111230055953719.jpg&h=f1388a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://aprilfashiondesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/img_5097_s-1.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faprilfashiondesign.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2Fimg_5097_s-1.png&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=4bff573e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://aprilfashiondesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/img_5097_s-1.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<img src=\"http://ttfaxing.com/uploadfile/2014/0403/201404042128075824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fttfaxing.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F0403%2F201404042128075824.jpg&h=a8adaacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年初中睇呢套劇<br />\n男人老狗都睇到流馬尿<br />\n幾肉酸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YrpNTUnlO14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYrpNTUnlO14&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=cf1935cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YrpNTUnlO14</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7K_08wQYJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV7K_08wQYJQ&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=56ef5e55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7K_08wQYJQ</a><br />\n<br />\nmsn -&gt; whatsapp<br />\n劇集潮 -&gt; 電視都唔會開<br />\nqooza xanga -&gt; 再無人玩<br />\n捉e因 爆旋陀螺 -&gt; 功課 興趣班 功課 興趣班<br />\n活到二字頭<br />\n回望番自己小學 中學真係開心過宜家好多<br />\n起碼唔洗諗以後層樓點算 買唔買得起車 養唔養得起樓<br />\n可惜 一切都已經係過去<br />\n聽番以前成日聽既歌 d回億湧哂上黎<br />\n再望住手頭上份assignment lecture notes<br />\n唉 繼續番去溫書啦 柒頭<br />\n<img src=\"http://i288.photobucket.com/albums/ll165/wingpoon/iodyxl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi288.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fll165%2Fwingpoon%2Fiodyxl.jpg&h=33ee4acd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94e2149df986a2ffe235503603bf261d14adcdeb","tid":151724,"uid":90587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"特別係msn時代<br />\n每日都係部電腦面前<br />\n捕住暗戀既女仔幾時上線<br />\n一上線就震佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔知點解以前既歌咁「coom」聽<br />\n雖然宜家一直都有keep住出好hit既歌<br />\n但聽一排就厭哂<br />\n以前簡簡單單既歌已經可以聽好耐<br />\n特別鐘意聽佢以前唱既歌<br />\n<br />\n有種好sad既感覺<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45moRuCH2qs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D45moRuCH2qs&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=55ec86cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45moRuCH2qs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7oIzHqJIORU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7oIzHqJIORU&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a41bdf42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7oIzHqJIORU</a>"},{"pid":"97942f9e36d67499294e248f6e9cee4fbc8e1bd0","tid":151724,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"大家都sent 短訊<br />\n隔空咁交流 已經好足夠<br />\n<br />\n好過宜家又ig 又sc<br />\n花花世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cb647e1bef1d1f4942b98ef34a0ac41d0ac3b0","tid":151724,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年一邊打cso一邊msn吹水<br />\n好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5549bb2faf87f17be795a364cb1d1c0437c5e582","tid":151724,"uid":27492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:24:02.000Z","msg":"係 日日放學跑返屋企等鐘意既人online msn<br />\n突登睇佢聽緊咩歌 同佢一齊聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11515809475bf88563066fe9a1a1c05557f7ceb6","tid":151724,"uid":90587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"聽緊 楊丞琳首 匿名的好友<br />\n諗番起當年同暗戀既人一齊睇呢套劇<br />\n有講有笑<br />\n諗番起佢睇到睇濕濕既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜宜家佢已經去左外國<br />\n再搵唔番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a64f9bf47d8e95b20a22083d95980b40199dc82","tid":151724,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T19:25:59.000Z","msg":"香港只會愈黎愈差<br />\n10年後就會有人問<br />\n覺唔覺2016-19係人生最開心既時期"},{"pid":"70dbf7e3d4f572fc54624f9492f9730c7a68161b","tid":151724,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港只會愈黎愈差<br />\n10年後就會有人問<br />\n覺唔覺2016-19係人生最開心既時期</blockquote><br />\nTrue<br />\n唔知幾時開始少左份人情味<br />\n生活仲變得更加不快樂"},{"pid":"4702cdde2af813bd399df1089ba1a254379edbf6","tid":151724,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a608d8f8708a6d5f1b57024308b533be89a4b724","tid":151724,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"我想返12歲之前<br />\n06 OK<br />\n07就不了"},{"pid":